videos.headline: Finley runs it in for a TD
videos.description: Ryan Finley keeps the ball himself and gets in the end zone for a Wolfpack touchdown late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Wake Forest makes two wild catches in a row
videos.description: Wake Forest receivers first make a one-handed catch and then a leaping catch back-to-back to get the Demon Deacons' first touchdown of the night.

videos.headline: Emezie finds the end zone
videos.description: Ryan Finley gets the ball to Emeka Emezie who breaks a tackle on his way to a fourth quarter Wolfpack touchdown.

videos.headline: NC State answers with one-handed catch
videos.description: After two ridiculous catches by Wake Forest, NC State answers with a crazy one-handed catch of their own.

videos.headline: Newman finds Dortch for Wake Forest TD
videos.description: Jamie Newman finds Greg Dortch late in the fourth quarter to shorten Wake Forest's deficit.
